"pid":"3849d1c2a668e6eee9456780edac8450f311a6ca","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"人地派個死士出嚟比人打<br />\n<br />\n連打人嘅都可能係佢地嘅人<br />\n<br />\n但係你哋就即刻同前線割蓆<br />\n<br />\nCls"},{"pid":"b2f7e9c09eba18bd3e478d10d05d5c8490c27bd5","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"各位幫手推"},{"pid":"318945f61daeb67831e71f48e5a95b02786e86e0","tid":1466482,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"唔完美 可接受"},{"pid":"6b672d4dc6f86b302b9f4926057d875dff768428","tid":1466482,"uid":16073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"不割"},{"pid":"2bc15646ac021e21ebe753a79ffe51ee5e2eb36b","tid":1466482,"uid":100787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"屌個熱門全部輸 女義士比人蓋過左？<br />\n槍口對外 不分不割<br />\n槍口對外 不分不割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dece059ac4d0f503720f7493c70af4c0b6ad8a8c","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"不割！"},{"pid":"530270a7ab67d1ff19c221544521c7c60494fd16","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"已經冇人記得女義士"},{"pid":"173ec0acf0cd7623ef1f700ea8c821f3acadee09","tid":1466482,"uid":56238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"其實現埸d手足可多些同外國記者交談，遇到同樣事件外國抗爭者點處理，攞多d經驗。"},{"pid":"44f40b22c7bfbb59bdf4e928ba90e86eea6146b9","tid":1466482,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"9251596d0b386a1bfa83c69b738697132615e4d8","tid":1466482,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"機場一役喺要喺「公安」同「醫護第一」之間取決一方，從而比對家分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對中共黎講犧牲一個公安<br />\n同收買一個金毛MK仔同收買啲人扮勇武掉野去警車唔係無可能<br />\n搵幾個人就挑起到你地內鬥<br />\n圍左公安咁耐有無得著？對五大訴求有無幫助？<br />\n唔喺幫個公安講說話，而喺處事要為大局著想<br />\n圍左三、四個鐘頭先上到醫護車<br />\n之後個金毛MK仔即刻第一時間沖出馬路靜坐阻路<br />\n我就覺得成年事好鬼鬼<br />\n根本喺一場中共/黑警Show<br />\n最大敵人根本就係你地自己<br />\n要時刻都有批判性思考<br />\n入得機場和理非就和理非<br />\n比中共睇穿你班人「好憎公安」同「讓路比醫護」兩者之間做出決定<br />\n萬死個公安死左就有位比人入<br />\n但就係咁比人分化你話抵唔抵？"},{"pid":"84bdf3f2a4301451a6546b0bf2e85f9d7298b2cc","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"共產黨派一個記者<br />\n幾個公安<br />\n就成功分割港豬"},{"pid":"ab6814a592894c4c258ba4ffa9fc01127262b7a1","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"393330ee39c1e2e4dd38e0f752be6a7a125f3379","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68112b3e5f0916326cbc0228f385ea56061c5f14","tid":1466482,"uid":8535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"內鬼不嬲都有，最重要係大家目標一致<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"cdc01c6322ebb1e008658ae98fdd341409350fc1","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc4a1392e4c863d5ba8cb9b391240f67e20c8879","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8fb04713be7c8986115dbd7fb664519738af53a0","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38e773127d68e3fae137fdcd35bfc3c3423f03f0","tid":1466482,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"